        <div class="absolute top-3 right-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-orange-500/70">⚠️ Dictionary-Dependent</div>
        <p class="text-2xl font-black text-white tracking-wider mb-2">MM</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-orange-300 font-semibold mb-3">6 points · M=3, M=3 · Interjection: pleasure/agreement</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">MM is SOWPODS-only and contains no vowels. It's the highest-scoring vowelless 2-letter word at 6 points (tied with no others). TWL players cannot use this word — check which dictionary your game uses before playing.</p>
      </div>

