        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Only 2 M tiles exist:</span> There are only 2 M tiles in the entire bag. If you have both, your opponent has none. Playing MM uses both simultaneously — which may or may not be optimal depending on whether longer M words (MAKE, MONEY, MAZE) are available.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

